headline: FleishmanHillard Announces Wave of New Global Leadership Appointments
summary: FleishmanHillard today announced several key roles as a part of its global leadership team under recently appointed President and CEO J.J. Carter. These individuals will be responsible for defining critical growth areas and operational priorities as the firm continues its evolution.

headline: MERCURY PUBLIC AFFAIRS ANNOUNCES MERGER WITH SERAFIN & ASSOCIATES
summary: Leading national bipartisan public strategy firm Mercury Public Affairs (Mercury), today announced that Chicago-based Serafin & Associates (Serafin) is merging into Mercury's Illinois business, which will expand the firm's public affairs and strategic communications capabilities in the Midwest and nationwide.
